     ```html
     <form action="/comments/new" method="post">
       <textarea placeholder="Enter comment here..."></textarea>
       <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{ csrf_token }}" />
       <input type="submit" value="Submit">
     </form>
     ```
